title: Spaghetti Aglio e Olio
description: Classic Italian pasta with garlic, olive oil, and chili flakes.
steps: 1. Cook spaghetti until al dente. 2. Sauté garlic and chili in olive oil. 3. Toss with pasta and parsley.

title: Chicken Caesar Salad
description: Crisp romaine lettuce with grilled chicken, croutons, and Caesar dressing.
steps: 1. Grill chicken and slice. 2. Toss lettuce with dressing. 3. Add chicken, croutons, and Parmesan.

title: Vegan Tofu Stir-Fry
description: Tofu and vegetables cooked in soy sauce and sesame oil.
steps: 1. Stir-fry tofu until golden. 2. Add vegetables and sauce. 3. Serve with rice.

title: Beef Tacos
description: Mexican-style tacos with spiced beef and toppings.
steps: 1. Cook beef with spices. 2. Fill taco shells and top with veggies and cheese.

title: Avocado Toast
description: Toasted bread topped with smashed avocado and seasoning.
steps: 1. Toast bread. 2. Mash avocado with lemon juice. 3. Spread and season.

title: Tom Yum Soup
description: Spicy and sour Thai soup with shrimp and lemongrass.
steps: 1. Boil broth with herbs. 2. Add shrimp and mushrooms. 3. Season with lime and chili.

title: Margherita Pizza
description: Classic pizza with tomato sauce, mozzarella, and basil.
steps: 1. Spread sauce over dough. 2. Add cheese and basil. 3. Bake until golden.

title: Beef Stroganoff
description: Creamy beef and mushroom dish served with pasta.
steps: 1. Cook beef and mushrooms. 2. Stir in sour cream. 3. Serve over pasta.

title: Greek Salad
description: Fresh salad with feta, olives, and cucumber.
steps: 1. Chop veggies. 2. Toss with olive oil and oregano. 3. Top with feta.

title: Banana Pancakes
description: Fluffy pancakes made with mashed bananas.
steps: 1. Mix ingredients. 2. Cook on skillet. 3. Serve warm with syrup.

title: Butter Chicken
description: Creamy Indian chicken curry with tomato and spices.
steps: 1. Marinate chicken. 2. Cook in tomato-butter sauce. 3. Add cream and serve.

title: Garlic Fried Rice
description: Fragrant rice stir-fried with garlic and soy sauce.
steps: 1. Sauté garlic. 2. Add rice and soy sauce. 3. Stir-fry and garnish.

title: Grilled Salmon
description: Simple grilled salmon with lemon and herbs.
steps: 1. Marinate salmon. 2. Grill until cooked. 3. Serve with lemon slices.

title: Caprese Salad
description: Italian salad with tomato, mozzarella, and basil.
steps: 1. Slice tomato and mozzarella. 2. Layer with basil. 3. Drizzle with oil and vinegar.

title: Shrimp Fried Rice
description: Quick fried rice with shrimp, egg, and peas.
steps: 1. Scramble egg. 2. Add shrimp and veggies. 3. Mix in rice and sauce.

title: Chocolate Brownies
description: Rich, fudgy chocolate brownies.
steps: 1. Mix ingredients. 2. Bake until set. 3. Cool before cutting.

title: Pumpkin Soup
description: Smooth pumpkin soup with cream and spices.
steps: 1. Cook pumpkin and onion. 2. Blend with broth. 3. Stir in cream and season.

title: Fish and Chips
description: Crispy battered fish with fries.
steps: 1. Coat fish in batter. 2. Deep-fry with fries. 3. Serve hot.

title: Chicken Fried Rice
description: Rice stir-fried with chicken, egg, and vegetables.
steps: 1. Fry egg and chicken. 2. Add rice and veggies. 3. Toss with sauce.

title: Eggplant Parmesan
description: Baked eggplant layered with cheese and tomato sauce.
steps: 1. Bread and bake eggplant. 2. Layer with sauce and cheese. 3. Bake again.

title: Pad Thai
description: Thai-style stir-fried noodles with tamarind sauce and peanuts.
steps: 1. Soak noodles. 2. Stir-fry with sauce and toppings. 3. Garnish with peanuts.

title: Beef Burger
description: Juicy grilled beef patty in a toasted bun.
steps: 1. Grill patty. 2. Assemble burger with toppings. 3. Serve warm.

title: Vegetable Curry
description: Spicy coconut-based curry with mixed vegetables.
steps: 1. Cook vegetables with curry paste. 2. Add coconut milk. 3. Simmer until thick.

title: Chicken Noodle Soup
description: Comforting chicken soup with noodles and vegetables.
steps: 1. Boil chicken and vegetables. 2. Add noodles. 3. Simmer until tender.

title: Mushroom Risotto
description: Creamy risotto with mushrooms and Parmesan.
steps: 1. Cook onion and rice. 2. Add broth gradually. 3. Stir in mushrooms and cheese.

title: Teriyaki Chicken
description: Glazed chicken in sweet-savory teriyaki sauce.
steps: 1. Cook chicken. 2. Add sauce and reduce. 3. Garnish with sesame seeds.

title: French Toast
description: Bread soaked in egg and milk, fried until golden.
steps: 1. Dip bread in mixture. 2. Fry until golden. 3. Serve with syrup.

title: Cauliflower Soup
description: Smooth cauliflower soup with cream and garlic.
steps: 1. Cook cauliflower. 2. Blend with cream. 3. Season and serve.

title: Chicken Wrap
description: Grilled chicken and veggies in a tortilla wrap.
steps: 1. Grill chicken. 2. Fill tortilla with ingredients. 3. Roll tightly.

title: Garlic Butter Shrimp
description: Juicy shrimp cooked in garlic butter sauce.
steps: 1. Melt butter and sauté garlic. 2. Add shrimp. 3. Cook until pink.

title: Avocado Smoothie
description: Creamy smoothie with avocado and milk.
steps: 1. Blend all ingredients. 2. Serve chilled.

title: Beef Ramen
description: Japanese noodle soup with beef and soy broth.
steps: 1. Cook noodles and beef. 2. Add broth and soy sauce. 3. Serve hot.

title: Falafel Wrap
description: Crispy falafel with tahini sauce in a pita wrap.
steps: 1. Blend ingredients. 2. Fry falafel. 3. Wrap with tahini and salad.

title: Tomato Soup
description: Classic tomato soup with basil and cream.
steps: 1. Cook tomato and onion. 2. Blend smooth. 3. Stir in cream.

title: Grilled Cheese Sandwich
description: Golden, melted cheese sandwich.
steps: 1. Butter bread. 2. Grill with cheese inside. 3. Serve hot.

title: Chicken Burrito Bowl
description: Rice bowl with grilled chicken, beans, and salsa.
steps: 1. Cook chicken. 2. Assemble all ingredients in a bowl. 3. Serve.

title: Vegetable Stir-Fry
description: Mixed vegetables stir-fried in soy sauce.
steps: 1. Heat oil. 2. Add vegetables and sauce. 3. Stir-fry until crisp.

title: Pesto Pasta
description: Pasta tossed in basil pesto sauce.
steps: 1. Blend pesto. 2. Toss with pasta. 3. Serve warm.

title: Beef Lasagna
description: Layered pasta with beef, cheese, and tomato sauce.
steps: 1. Layer sauce, pasta, and cheese. 2. Bake until bubbly.

title: Vegan Buddha Bowl
description: Nutritious bowl with quinoa, roasted veggies, and tahini sauce.
steps: 1. Roast veggies. 2. Assemble bowl. 3. Drizzle with tahini.
